his confirmation hearings.

01:53.567 --> 01:56.033
- Yes, Jeff Sessions,
Trump's attorney general

01:56.033 --> 01:58.233
and the unfortunate result
of Dobby the house-elf's

01:58.233 --> 02:00.700
