with a Confederate flag,

02:00.700 --> 02:03.333
got in trouble this--
enjoy--

02:03.333 --> 02:04.867
got in trouble this week

02:04.867 --> 02:07.734
for undisclosed meetings
with Russia's ambassador,

02:07.734 --> 02:10.533
