is not against the law.

02:10.533 --> 02:13.233
The problem is,
Sessions's confirmation hearing

02:13.233 --> 02:15.533
featured this exchange.

02:15.533 --> 02:18.266
- If there is any evidence
that anyone

02:18.266 --> 02:21.133
affiliated
with the Trump campaign

02:21.133 --> 02:23.633
communicated
with the Russian government

02:23.633 --> 02:25.100
in the course of this campaign,

02:25.100 --> 02:28.066
what will you do?

02:28.066 --> 02:32.767
- Senator Franken, I'm not aware
of, um, any of those activities.

02:32.767 --> 02:35.033
I have been called a surrogate

02:35.033 --> 02:37.000
at a time or two
in that campaign,

02:37.000 --> 02:39.133
and I didn't have--
not have communications

02:39.133 --> 02:40.934
with the Russians, um,

02:40.934 --> 02:42.934
and I'm unable to comment on it.

02:42.934 --> 02:44.800
- Now, there is an obvious
problem there.

02:44.800 --> 02:47.266
